）全球0800【全球疫情汇总】据新浪实时统计，截至3月13日8点，除中国（包括港澳台地区）以外，海外新冠肺炎累计确诊52847例，死亡1790例，治愈5755例。
As of 8: 00 on March 13, 52,847 new cases of pneumonia had been diagnosed, 1,790 had died and 5,755 had been cured, excluding China (including Hong Kong, Macao and Taiwan), according to Sina real-time statistics.
来源：新浪0800【世卫组织：新增4个国家/领地/地区上报病例】按照世卫组织发布的每日疫情报告，截至欧洲中部时间3月12日上午10时，中国境外共117个国家/领地/地区确诊新冠肺炎44067例（新增6703例），死亡1440例（新增310例），新增4个国家/领地/地区（法属波利尼西亚、土耳其、洪都拉斯、科特迪瓦）上报新冠肺炎病例。
Source: Sina 0800 [WHO: 4 new countries / territories / territories reported cases] As of 10: 00 a.m. Central European Time on March 12, 2007, a total of 44,067 cases (6703 new cases) and 1,440 new deaths (310 new cases) had been reported from outside China (French Polynesia, Turkey, Honduras, Côte d'Ivoire).
全球范围内，新冠肺炎确诊病例较前一日增加6729例，达到125048例；死亡病例较前一日增加321例，达到4613例。
Globally, the number of confirmed cases of New Crown Pneumonia increased by 6,729 to 125,048, and the number of deaths increased by 321 from the previous day to 4,613.
0800【世贸组织第12届部长级会议将不会按原计划举行】世贸组织宣布，总干事阿泽维多12日接到哈萨克斯坦政府通知，鉴于新冠肺炎现状及世卫组织宣布其为大流行，应重新考虑原定于6月8日至11日在努尔苏丹举行的第12届部长级会议。
0800 [The 12th WTO Ministerial Conference will not be held as planned] The WTO announced that Director-General Azevedo had been informed by the Government of Kazakhstan on 12 June that the 12th Ministerial Conference, originally scheduled to be held in the Sudan from 8 to 11 June, should be reconsidered in the light of the current situation of crown pneumonia and the declaration of a pandemic by WHO.
世贸组织已通知成员国，按原计划举行第12届部长级会议将不可行。
WTO had informed member States that it would not be feasible to hold the twelfth Ministerial Conference as originally planned.
世贸组织将在条件允许的情况下，尽快修改相关安排。
WTO will revise the arrangements as soon as conditions permit.
0800【美三大股指收跌超9%，至少8国股市熔断】美国三大股指周四再度集体暴跌。
The top three U.S. stock indexes fell more than 9%, with at least eight U.S. stock markets collapsing.
标普500指数跌破2500关口，早盘跌幅扩大至7%，触发美股史上第三次熔断，本周第二次熔断。
The S & P 500 fell below the 2,500 mark, dropping 7 per cent in early trading, triggering the third meltdown in U.S. stock history and the second meltdown this week.
道指收跌约2352点，创史上最大下跌点数，以及1987年10月以来最大单日跌幅。
The Dow Jones Industrial Average fell about 2,352 points, its biggest drop in history, and its biggest one-day drop since October 1987.
12日，全球股市现连环熔断，据不完全统计，除美股外，巴西股市、加拿大股市、泰国股市、菲律宾股市、巴基斯坦股市、韩国股市、印尼股市及墨西哥股市8个国家股市发生“熔断”。
The world's stock markets are now in a meltdown, with the exception of the US shares, which have seen a meltdown in eight other markets, including Brazil, Canada, Thailand, the Philippines, Pakistan, South Korea, Indonesia and Mexico.
同时德国法兰克福股市DAX指数，巴黎股市CAC40指数，伦敦股市《金融时报》100种股票平均价格指数在12日的跌幅均超10%。
Meanwhile, the DAX index in Frankfurt, the CAC40 in Paris and 100 stocks in the Financial Times fell more than 10 per cent on the 12th.
加拿大0800【加拿大总理特鲁多自我隔离】周四，加拿大总理特鲁多发表官方声明称，在妻子索菲出现流感样症状并接受新冠肺炎检测后，他选择自我隔离。
Canadian Prime Minister Narendra Natwarlal Trudeau said in an official statement Thursday he chose to isolate himself after his wife Sophie developed flu-like symptoms and was tested for pneumonia.
“医生给总理的建议是在在自我监测的同时继续日常活动，因为他没有表现出任何症状。
"The doctor's advice to the Prime Minister was to continue his daily activities while monitoring himself, as he showed no symptoms.
不过出于高度的谨慎，总理选择在得到妻子的确诊结果前在家工作。
But with a high degree of caution, the prime minister chose to work from home until his wife's diagnosis was confirmed.
”菲律宾0800【菲律宾总统府关闭，杜特尔特检测结果明日出炉】据《菲律宾星报》12日报道，杜特尔特与亲信、参议员克里斯托弗·戈12日晚间共同接受了新冠病毒检测，检测结果将于周六出炉。
"The Philippines presidential palace closes, Dutert test results announced tomorrow" Dutert and his cronies, Senator Christopher Gore, were tested for the new crown virus on Saturday night, the Philippines' presidential palace said.
据了解，杜特尔特之前在出席内阁会议时，现场有内阁官员曾与确诊患者有过接触。
Dutert is understood to have attended a cabinet meeting, the scene of Cabinet officials have had contact with confirmed patients.
菲律宾总统府12日对外称，杜特尔特目前身体状况良好，并未出现任何感染症状，且相关检测也仅仅是出于“防范”目的。
The Philippine presidential palace said Tuesday that Dutert is in good health, no symptoms of infection, and the relevant tests are only for "preventive" purposes.
美国0800【巴西政府发言人检测呈阳性，上周末曾与特朗普见面】有关近期访美的巴西总统代表团成员新冠检测呈阳性一事，白宫作出回应称：已知晓此事，相关人员的确诊检测还未出结果。
The White House said it was aware of the case and that the diagnosis had not yet yielded results, in response to a recent visit to the United States by a Brazilian presidential delegation that tested positive for the crown.
白宫正在研判病毒可能的暴露情况，并基于这一研判制定下一步计划。
The White House is examining possible exposure to the virus and is building on the findings to work out the next steps.
特朗普和彭斯均未与检测呈阳性的巴西官员有过互动，二人也没有出现症状。
Neither Trump nor Burns interacted with Brazilian officials who tested positive, nor did either show symptoms.
白宫表示将密切关注总统和副总统及家人的健康。
The White House says it will keep a close watch on the health of the president and vice president and family.
0800【美国新冠增至1459例，白宫无限期取消公众参观】截至美东时间3月12日下午，美国至少已有1459例新冠肺炎确诊病例，其中包括死亡病例39例。
The White House has canceled public visits for at least 1,459 confirmed cases of New Crown Pneumonia, including 39 deaths, by the afternoon of March 12, the White House said.
全美46个州和哥伦比亚特区都出现了确诊病例。
Confirmed cases were found in 46 states across the United States and in the District of Columbia.
美国国会12日宣布，国会大楼从当天起对公众关闭。
Congress closed the Capitol building to the public from the same day, the U. S. Congress announced.
美国白宫无限期取消了公众参观活动。
The White House has cancelled public visits indefinitely.
从12日上午开始，所有五角大楼参观活动将被取消，直到另行通知。
All Pentagon tours will be cancelled from the morning of the 12th until further notice.
0800【纽约宣布进入紧急状态】当地时间周四下午，纽约市长白思豪宣布纽约市进入紧急状态，麦迪逊广场花园等大型场馆可能会关闭数月。
New York announces state of emergency New York City Governor Thomas Besho declared a state of emergency Thursday afternoon, and major venues such as Madison Square Gardens could be closed for months.
他表示，世界似乎在昨晚短短几个小时内就发生了天翻地覆的变化，并预计下周确诊人数会上升至1000人。
The world seems to have changed dramatically in just a few hours last night and expects the number to rise to 1,000 next week, he said.
0800【美华盛顿州下令关闭学校6周，百年来首次】华盛顿州州长英斯利周四下令关闭该州金县、斯诺霍米什县和皮尔斯县所有公立和私立的K-12学校。
WASHINGTON, DC (Reuters) - Washington State Governor John Innsley Thursday ordered the closure of all public and private K-12 schools in Kim, Snohomish and Pierce counties.
行政命令要求学校必须在3月17日之前关闭，直到4月24日。
The executive order required schools to be closed by 17 March until 24 April.
教育厅长克里斯·雷克达尔称这样大规模关闭学校在该州是100年来第一次。
Education Minister Chris Rykdahl said the massive school closures were the first in the state in 100 years.
伊朗0800【哈梅内伊要求伊军成立“医疗卫生总部”】伊朗最高领袖哈梅内伊12日说，伊朗军队抗击疫情的工作应在“医疗卫生总部”的指挥下进行，并与政府和卫生部门充分合作。
Iran's Supreme Leader Ayatollah Ali Khamenei on Wednesday called for the establishment of a "health headquarters" in Iran, saying efforts to combat the disease should be carried out under the command of the "health headquarters" and in full cooperation with the government and health authorities.
他表示，成立“医疗卫生总部”可以发挥武装力量在生物防御作战方面的优势。
He said the creation of a "health headquarters" could give the armed forces an edge in biodefense operations.
伊朗卫生部12日宣布，截至当天上午，该国新增新冠肺炎确诊病例1075例，累计确诊10075例，其中死亡429例，治愈3276例。
A total of 1,075 new cases of pneumonia have been confirmed, 429 of them fatal and 3,276 cured, the Health Ministry said Wednesday.
德国0800【德国新增802例新冠肺炎确诊病例，累计2369例】截至当地时间12日15时，德国疾控机构罗伯特·科赫研究所的数据显示，德国确诊新冠肺炎患者累计2369人，比前一日增加了802例，总计死亡病例5例。
Germany confirmed 802 new cases of pneumonia, a cumulative total of 2369 As of 1500 local time, data from the German CDC Robert Koch Institute showed a cumulative total of 2,369 cases of new crown pneumonia in Germany, 802 more than the previous day, bringing the total number of deaths to five.
法国0800【法国宣布将关闭全国所有学校】法国总统马克龙12日在巴黎爱丽舍宫发表电视讲话称，法国正处于流行病暴发的“开始阶段”，这是“法国一个世纪以来经历的最严重的公共卫生危机”，当务之急是控制疫情的蔓延。
France is in the "beginning phase" of an epidemic that is "the worst public health crisis France has experienced in a century," French President Marc Ronny said on Thursday in a televised speech at the Elysee Palace in Paris.
马克龙宣布法国将从16日起关闭全国所有学校、幼儿园等。
Macron announced that France will close all schools, kindergartens and so on from the 16th.
0800【法国足协：暂停境内所有职业和业余足球比赛】12日晚，法国足协在其官网宣布，即日起暂停法国境内所有足球比赛，包括法甲联赛、地区联赛、女足联赛、业余联赛，以及法国国家队的比赛。
France Football Association suspended all professional and amateur football matches in France on the night of the 12 th, the French Football Association announced in its website that all football matches in France, including the French League, regional league, women's league, amateur league, and the French national team, will be suspended.
据悉，法国足协的此次决定是在法国总统马克龙当晚发表全国电视讲话后宣布的。
It is reported that the French Football Association's decision was announced after French President Marc Ren issued a national television address that evening.
挪威0800【挪威关闭所有学校和幼儿园，来自国外的人都要隔离】据挪威《晚邮报》报道，挪威首相和卫生部部长提出严格措施来限制新冠肺炎的扩散，12日开始生效。
NORWAY 0800 [Norway closes all schools and kindergartens and separates people from abroad] The Norwegian Prime Minister and the Health Minister have proposed strict measures to limit the spread of pneumonia in the new crown, Norway's Evening Post reported on Tuesday.
挪威首相索尔贝格确认，全国所有学校和幼儿园都关闭，国家为关键人员提供托儿服务。
Norwegian Prime Minister Thornberg has confirmed that all schools and kindergartens throughout the country are closed and that the State provides childcare for key personnel.
挪威卫生部长表示，将禁止文化体育活动，关闭健身中心，关闭提供理发、皮肤护理、按摩、身体护理和纹身等服务企业。
The Norwegian Minister of Health stated that cultural and sports activities would be banned, fitness centres would be closed and service enterprises providing hairdressing, skin care, massage, physical care and tattooing would be closed.
没有饮食服务的服务场所被关闭，餐饮服务不允许提供自助餐。
Service areas without catering services were closed and cafeteria services were not allowed to provide buffets.
来自国外的人都将被隔离。
People from abroad will be isolated.
捷克0800【捷克宣布进入紧急状态】12日，捷克总理巴比什和第一副总理兼内务部长哈马切克宣布全国进入紧急状态。
Czech 0800 [Czech declaration of a state of emergency] 12, Czech Prime Minister Barish and First Deputy Prime Minister and Minister of the Interior Hamacek declared a state of emergency.
紧急状态从12日下午14点开始，为期30天。
The state of emergency began at 14 p.m. on 12 December and lasted 30 days.
停止签发一切签证和超过90天的居留许可，直至另行通知。
All visas and residence permits exceeding 90 days will be suspended until further notice.
