Colombia announces a state of health emergency President Duke of Colombia has declared a health emergency since December 12, taking into account the number of confirmed cases of pneumonia in Colombia and the World Health Organization's declaration of a pandemic.
截至12日上午，哥伦比亚累计报告9例新冠肺炎确诊病例。
