Spain's second cabinet member has been confirmed to be infected with the new crown virus (Ncrown Virus) by Carolyn Darias, Spain's Minister for Territorial Policy and Public Function, is the second member of the cabinet to become infected with the new crown virus since the minister for equality, according to the Spanish newspaper El Pais.
