目前，西班牙各自治区均已宣布暂时关闭学校，加泰罗尼亚自治区政府12日也宣布为防止疫情扩散，在未来两周内对该区疫情较为集中的4个市镇约7万居民进行封闭式管理，非必要情况禁止人员出入。
The autonomous communities of Spain have announced the temporary closure of schools and the Government of the Autonomous Community of Catalonia announced on 12 December that, in order to prevent the spread of the epidemic, some 70,000 residents of the four municipalities with concentrated epidemics in the region would be placed under closed management and not allowed to enter or leave the country if necessary.
