Turkey has closed its schools and sports competition closed to the public, President Karin announced on March 16 that primary, middle and high schools would be closed for one week, and students would receive distance education at home from March 23.
从3月16日起，大学放假三周。
The university was closed for three weeks from 16 March.
4月底之前，所有体育赛事不对观众开放。
By the end of April, all sporting events will be closed to spectators.
公职人员未经审批不得出国。
Public officials may not leave the country without authorization.
